{
  "texts": [
    "ConclusionIn this research, we propose the design of a GPT industrial bot to assist operators of a small factory in improving their daily working experience while integrating some basic I5.0 requirements, such as human well-being and ecosystem preservation.",
    "We design the industrial bot in an offline and online version.",
    "We connect the offline GPT bot model to the OpenAI GPT4-LM in its backend with their APIs and Langchain agents.",
    "We develop its front end using Streamlit, an open-source web-based visualization tool.",
    "We utilize the GPT-4 new feature for the online version to create customized GPTs based on specified requirements."
  ]
}